<use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wcw1719485700746.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wcw1719485700746.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wcw1719485700746.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mnd1665702602228\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $keyvalidation\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mnd1665702602228___keyvalidation_272234\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__topic_d85328e1_d85329e1_d85330e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__p_d85331e1_d85332e1_d85333e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyvalidation</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__section_w714ab1b7b5_w715ab1b7_w716ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__p_d85334e1_d85335e1_d85336e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">if ($keyvalidation (\"CUSTOMER\", 1) &gt; 0)</code> ...</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__topic_d56662e1_d56663e1_d56664e1_d56665e1_d56666e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d540440e91\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e20__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e20__entry__3\">Entity name.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e20__entry__2\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e20__entry__3\"> Key identifier; the value will be\n\t\t\t\t truncated to form an integer. <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e80\">1, the primary key.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__d6103e83\">2, 3, 4, and so on, the number that\n\t\t\t\t\t\tidentifies a candidate key that has been defined for <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>. </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__topic_d56667e1_d56668e1_d56669e1_d56670e1_d56671e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d540440e172\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8969e1_d8970e1_d8971e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyvalidation</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8969e1_d8970e1_d8971e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8969e1_d8970e1_d8971e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8969e1_d8970e1_d8971e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8969e1_d8970e1_d8971e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8969e1_d8970e1_d8971e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8969e1_d8970e1_d8971e1__entry__2\">\n No validation is required.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8969e1_d8970e1_d8971e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8969e1_d8970e1_d8971e1__entry__2\">\n Key requires validation.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following this\n            Function</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\"> Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The entity name provided is not a valid\n\t\t\t\t name or the entity is not present in the component structure. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1104</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_KEY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The specified key is not valid; for\n\t\t\t\t example, the key number was out of range. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1128</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_NOT_A_KEY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnd1665702602228__table_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The specified key is an index.\n\t\t\t\t </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__topic_d56672e1_d56673e1_d56674e1_d56675e1_d56676e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d540440e366\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__d6417e20\">Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__topic_d56677e1_d56678e1_d56679e1_d56680e1_d56681e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d540440e375\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__p_d85352e1_d85353e1_d85354e1\">A key needs validation in either of the following circumstances:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__li_d34637e1_d34638e1_d34639e1\">Data in one of the fields that makes up the key has been modified (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keymod</span> is 1), but has not yet been successfully validated (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyvalidation</span> is also 1).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__li_d34640e1_d34641e1_d34642e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span> is 1, regardless of the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyvalidation</span>.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__section_a55_zjj_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d540440e405\">Example: Validating Keys </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyvalidation</span>\n            function:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mnd1665702602228__pre_hrp_1kj_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; for each key\n; if validation is pending,\n; do it\n; uh-oh\n; next key, please\nvEntity = \"CUSTOMER\"\nvKey = 1\nwhile ( vKey &lt;= $totkeys(vEntity ))\n if ($keyvalidation (vEntity , vKey ) &gt; 0)\n validatekey vEntity , vKey \n if ($status &lt; 0)\n return -1\n endif\n endif\n vKey = vKey + 1\nendwhile\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwi1665702576586.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatefield</a><p>Validate a field of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1665702576817.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatekey</a><p>Validate a key of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702576896.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validateocc</a><p>Validate an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpz1719812992669.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occvalidation</a><p>Check whether an occurrence requires validation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424407\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424407\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$keyvalidation Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $keyvalidation Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation. $keyvalidation ( Entity , KeyNumber ) Example: if ($keyvalidation (\"CUSTOMER\", 1) > 0) ... Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. KeyNumber Numeric Key identifier; the value will be truncated to form an integer. 1, the primary key. 2, 3, 4, and so on, the number that identifies a candidate key that has been defined for Entity . Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $keyvalidation Value Meaning \"\" An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. 0 No validation is required. 1 Key requires validation. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following this Function Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not present in the component structure. -1104 <UPROCERR_KEY> The specified key is not valid; for example, the key number was out of range. -1128 <UPROCERR_NOT_A_KEY> The specified key is an index. Use Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports. Description A key needs validation in either of the following circumstances: Data in one of the fields that makes up the key has been modified ( $keymod is 1), but has not yet been successfully validated ( $keyvalidation is also 1). $keycheck is 1, regardless of the value of $keyvalidation . Example: Validating Keys The following example uses the $keyvalidation function: ; for each key ; if validation is pending, ; do it ; uh-oh ; next key, please vEntity = \"CUSTOMER\" vKey = 1 while ( vKey <= $totkeys(vEntity )) if ($keyvalidation (vEntity , vKey ) > 0) validatekey vEntity , vKey if ($status < 0) return -1 endif endif vKey = vKey + 1 endwhile Copy Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). validatefield Validate a field of the current occurrence. validatekey Validate a key of the current occurrence. validateocc Validate an occurrence. $occvalidation Check whether an occurrence requires validation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}